text: Karijoki is a municipality in Southern Ostrobothnia, Finland. As of 28 February 2023, 1,192 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Isojoki, Kauhajoki, Kristiinankaupunki and Teuva. == Villages == * Alakylä * Karijoen kirkonkylä * Myrkky * Ylikylä == Other websites == * Municipality of Karijoki – Official website Category:Municipalities of South Ostrobothnia
